nodes.text: Feat of Clay: Inside Kotobukiya is an article appearing in Star Wars Insider 99, with interviews and translations by Shingo Nakagawa and Mariko Kawamura. The piece details the creation of Kotobukiya's newest line of clay models, the Bounty Hunter Series, including models for those bounty hunters seen in the film Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back—4-LOM, Zuckuss, Bossk, Dengar, IG-88, and Boba Fett.
